data.description: Pretty 3-2-2 built by renowned DR Horton Homes, located in Ft. Worth with the Eagle Mountain ISD, close to major shopping, schools, & freeway for the commuter. Beautiful hardwood flooring in main areas, tile & carpeting in other areas of the home. Fresh paint inside. Sellers had solar panels installed & will submit the paperwork on the contract & it will be paid off at closing. Large master bedroom  with attached Texas style bath with walk in closet. Great neighborhood with all the community ammenities you could imagine, enjoy the community pool which is across from the home, just walk across the street & no worries about maintenance, just enjoy & meet your neighbors. Enjoy those low utility bills
